{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0663ed8304","title":"复周恩来电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3b0515125","index":0,"year":1942,"month":8,"day":17,"articleId":"0663ed8304"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"300d6633dc","type":"paragraph","text":"复周恩来电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"0663ed8304"},{"id":"8b8d4c766b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年8月17日）毛现患感冒不能启程，拟派林彪同志赴西安见蒋，请征蒋同意，如能征得将同意带你至西安，你回延面谈一次，随即借林或朱赴西安见蒋则更好。[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央书记处起草的复周恩未电的主要内容。周恩来8月14日应约会见介石。蒋提出拟在西安药毛泽东一谈。当日周恩来格见蒋情况电告毛泽东，并说蒋欲见毛泽东的目的“未可测”。周提出两个办法：（一）以林范为代表，赴西安见蒋：（二）要求蒋借周至西安，然后周飞","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"0663ed8304"}],"page":{"id":"b89aa6aad5","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"0663ed8304","start":120,"end":120}}}},"__N_SSG":true}